WEBVTT

00:00:01.199 --> 00:00:10.799
I'm on late tonight; it's 10:00. I know I usually come on at 9:00. My friend Billy Burke called, and I was so excited.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:20.123
I'll never say I've got to get off the phone to do a broadcast when he calls, because I'm telling you, it's a stream of living water coming out of that man. What a blessing.

00:00:20.124 --> 00:00:42.479
I got to talk to him for over two hours tonight, and I cherish those times listening to the old stories of the generals he's had the pleasure to walk in the shadows of and the people he's been able to be around in ministry, like Kathryn Kuhlman and Ralph Wilkerson—all these great people.

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:48.639
It's amazing. I just go, 'Golly.'You know, I lose track of time.

00:00:48.640 --> 00:01:01.839
When you're talking to somebody like that and you're listening about the old people, you lose track of time and you go, 'My God, what an honor that you would call and talk to me when the Lord tells him to,'you know, just to encourage me to keep going.

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:05.919
He listens to us and prays with us, and it's a blessing that he would pray with us.

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:17.999
I have so many amazing people that come and pray—so many amazing men and women of God, big platforms, little platforms, all kinds of people all around the world that come and watch us and pray with us.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:30.228
I mean, what an honor. You know, God has called us, I guess, for such a time as this right now to do what we're doing, and I'm humbled by what the Lord has done.

00:01:30.229 --> 00:01:41.839
It's amazing. But I want to go—how many are here? Oh, we have more than enough.

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:49.138
All right, 1,900 right now. We'll start. Well, good evening everybody. Thank you for joining me.

00:01:49.139 --> 00:01:55.895
We're going to go over some of the news and what's going on today with the signs of the times and the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:01:55.896 --> 00:02:02.959
It's all around us. I'm telling you, Jesus Christ is coming, and I hope you have your anticipation out there.

00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:11.519
You know, it's like I said, talking to my friend. He said, 'So many people have said that for so long, so many years, all the time.

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:29.119
We've heard that.'But I asked him, 'Sir, do you believe Jesus is coming soon?'And he said, 'Brandon, I believe he could come back tomorrow.'That's as you watch the news, as you see the things happening all around us, you have an anticipation.

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:37.279
And even he was saying, 'I'm surprised he hadn't already come.'When you look at what's going on in the news, I believe he could come back tomorrow.

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:46.799
I believe he could come back this week. That's how soon I feel like it's coming. You can feel it inside, and it's cool to see it.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:03:17.359
As you see what happened today, as you see what's going on with America today, talking to him about the revival and talking to Billy about what he believes is coming—it's amazing to hear him talk because you know the Holy Spirit's going to lead us all in the same direction, just differently: different frames, different pictures, but we all get the same puzzle piece, right?

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:25.336
Talking about the portals and the revival, I would love for him to come on if he ever feels comfortable.

00:03:25.337 --> 00:03:44.603
I don't ever try to push things, but to talk about what he's seen about the healing miracles in his ministry with Kathryn Kuhlman and being around and seeing eyes open and ears open in his own ministry and flowing with the gift of the Spirit like he has.

00:03:44.604 --> 00:03:49.039
One day, I believe he will. But I'm so excited because he wants to do a meeting.

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:54.880
He's always talking about doing meetings and what the Lord is doing for this season of his life.

00:03:54.881 --> 00:04:06.889
You know, he's going into his 70s now, and this chapter where he's at, being an elder flowing in the gifts of the Spirit and where God has called him, it's amazing.

00:04:06.890 --> 00:04:14.559
Because I'm new and I'm just starting out, listening to somebody who's been in it for 50-some years, for us who are just cutting our teeth, we don't even know.

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:21.270
I feel like I'm just trying to find my bearings and going where God has me.

00:04:21.271 --> 00:04:30.478
It's amazing to hear about healings. I love to hear the testimonies of what Jesus has done for so many people.

00:04:30.479 --> 00:04:36.593
People think, 'Is healing still for today?'Yes, healing is for today.

00:04:36.594 --> 00:04:46.529
The delivering power of the Holy Spirit is still for today. He is the same yesterday, today, and forever. And what he did 2,000 years ago, he's still doing today.

00:04:46.530 --> 00:04:55.479
If you believe—I believe with all my heart—we're going to see some of the greatest miracles that we've ever seen before in the days ahead.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:05:11.889
I would say, 'Do you believe the revival will be all over America?'and he said, 'I believe it will be in pockets.'There'll be portals; that's exactly what I've seen.

00:05:11.890 --> 00:05:18.879
That's why I keep telling you I see a migration. There are so many people that will be moving.

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:24.819
Yeah, the Holy Spirit will be moving in areas, but there'll be some places that are greater than others.

00:05:24.820 --> 00:05:31.634
I have brought up Church of His Presence. John Kilpatrick—why I keep bringing up this man.

00:05:31.635 --> 00:05:36.594
I don't know this man, but I know him by the spirit of what I know in my spirit.

00:05:36.595 --> 00:05:51.359
When I pray for Church of His Presence, the Lord said that he did it once in his ministry and the well is not there like it was, but it's coming back in a greater capacity.

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:58.559
And he said, 'I'm renewing John Kilpatrick's health like youth is renewed like the eagles, and he will finish strong.

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:09.038
It's not time for him to go home yet.'He will be a person—I saw him sitting on the stage and the glory and the presence of the Lord filling Church of His Presence again.

00:06:09.039 --> 00:06:16.799
Then I saw places like a church in Minnesota. I saw a major move of God in a church in Minnesota.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:22.318
I saw Collinsville, where Pastor Chip and Candace are, and Branson.

00:06:22.319 --> 00:06:32.959
I saw I-35, Oklahoma City going down to Dallas-Fort Worth, a major move of God coming on the highway, I-35.

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:46.559
I've seen it out in the Crescent, Oklahoma area. I've seen it in places that you would least expect it, but it's because of the cultivation of prayer.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:51.839
Much prayer has gone up in these areas. It will come out of prayer; it's bathed in prayer.

00:06:51.840 --> 00:07:05.839
The one that I've seen in the Mabee Center with ORU and with the Victory over across the street with Paul Daugherty being the overflow—a major revival coming to Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:14.719
I believe that Tulsa is a hot spot for the end-time move. I believe there'll be areas that are stronger than others.

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:24.399
And even as I talked to my friend today, he said, 'Brandon, I believe that it won't be like that everywhere because not everybody wants it.

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:30.959
Not everybody wants to cultivate His presence. Nobody wants to pay the price in prayer. Not everybody wants that.

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:57.439
But there's a remnant of people that are hungry, that are desperate for a move of God in these last days, and you're about to see one of the greatest harvests of souls this world has ever seen before.'But I saw people migrating, and I saw properties in Tulsa, properties in areas where it will be so hard to even find rent houses because of the fact that people are just trying to get around the revival.

00:07:57.440 --> 00:08:02.541
Will it last a long time? I don't believe it will; I believe it'll be a quick work.

00:08:02.542 --> 00:08:06.399
But I saw a major move of God in Brazil and all these other areas.

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:11.702
And I keep talking about it—a new Azusa Street for Asia coming out of South Korea.

00:08:11.703 --> 00:08:16.159
Just talking that over. What was it like in the tent revival?

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:23.509
What was it like reading books from Kathryn Kuhlman and Oral Roberts and A.A.

00:08:23.510 --> 00:08:33.639
Allen and all these that walked before? Diana has been on a scavenger hunt lately going through the books.

00:08:33.639 --> 00:08:37.178
I think she's gotten probably ten new books in the last week.

00:08:37.179 --> 00:08:50.539
These are old books that are hardly printed anymore, that you can't find, and she finds them in certain places, looking for them to try to find books that are not in print anymore.

00:08:50.540 --> 00:08:58.852
Like, where are the books not in print? What did they read? How did they get where they got?

00:08:58.853 --> 00:09:06.052
I told her, "I love your brain, the way you think, baby."She's asking, "How did they get it?

00:09:06.053 --> 00:09:09.359
How was Kathryn Kuhlman inspired? What inspired her? What books did she read?

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:16.719
What inspired Oral Roberts to keep going? Where was he at when he first started, like us?

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:21.218
What inspired them to keep going? What fed their flame?"Yeah, the Bible.

00:09:21.219 --> 00:09:25.359
But there were people that you listen to and you glean from, like I do, Billy.

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:41.039
And you listen to them and you go, "Okay, I get it."Why try to learn it yourself and reinvent the wheel whenever somebody's already walked in it and they can tell you, "That doesn't work.

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:48.799
That didn't work for me,"versus the people who keep doing something and hit the wall?

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:55.005
You learn out of being dumb and you go, "Well, that really hurt."You know, the car door hurts when you slam your hand in it.

00:09:55.006 --> 00:10:03.679
Don't do that; that's dumb. Versus the one that says, "I've already done that; don't do that."So, I don't know.

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:14.799
I try to be encouraging to you all, but that's where I was tonight. That's why I'm late. But praise the Lord.

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:25.119
I want to show you some of the things that happened today in the news. The earthquakes are taking place.

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:32.559
And then what we saw last night about the metamorphosis, and the Lord showed us we're about to see something we've never seen before.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:38.299
We're about to see a butterfly fly out of the church that we've never seen before.

00:10:38.300 --> 00:10:50.479
I saw colors on a butterfly, a beautiful mosaic that was so beautiful and so vibrant.

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:58.639
And as I was looking through this cocoon, this caterpillar was inside, pushing with all its might.

00:10:58.640 --> 00:11:04.408
It represented the church, the body of Christ pushing with all its might.

00:11:04.409 --> 00:11:09.838
And I saw a breaking point of this caterpillar coming out of the cocoon as a beautiful new butterfly.

00:11:09.839 --> 00:11:15.599
And the Lord said, "Do you see that butterfly? It's something that you've never seen before.

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:21.945
What's about to happen with the church is something that you've never experienced before.

00:11:21.946 --> 00:11:43.919
It's colors on a mosaic you've never seen, a beautiful tapestry, a beautiful canvas of the Holy Spirit is about to be expressed in a way that the world has never seen before."Because it's His goodness and His mercy. As we say, "Show us Your glory, Lord.

00:11:43.920 --> 00:12:02.090
Give us an impartation of new demonstrations and manifestations of the glory that we've never seen before."I saw a blowing of goodness and mercy coming out of the Father's hand, and He blew on it and said it was just like Moses, Brandon.

00:12:02.091 --> 00:12:09.919
He said, "Show me Your glory,"and He let His goodness and His mercy pass by. And He said, "It's the goodness of God.

00:12:09.920 --> 00:12:17.199
It's the goodness of Me that brings man to repentance."It's My goodness and My mercy, Brandon.

00:12:17.200 --> 00:12:26.319
What you're about to see is a display of the goodness and the mercy of God like we've never seen before.

00:12:26.320 --> 00:12:33.759
It's His grace—an explosion, a tidal wave of the grace of God.

00:12:33.760 --> 00:12:51.159
I'm not talking about the grace where you say, "Well, Brandon, it's okay to live in sin and you can do this because God's grace covers it, brother."I'm not talking about living like a heathen and thinking you're going to experience the anointing and the presence of God.

00:12:51.160 --> 00:12:56.059
Be imitators of God as dear children. You've got to imitate the Lord.

00:12:56.060 --> 00:13:00.578
What is He doing? He isn't out there going to strip clubs and doing bad things.

00:13:00.579 --> 00:13:15.249
Be imitators of God as dear children; you be called and separate unto Him and say, "Listen, I'm sold out to You."Yeah, as a child we can fall down and skin our knee, but we don't live there.

00:13:15.250 --> 00:13:26.512
We pick ourselves back up, brush it off, put some antiseptic on it, and we keep looking to Him, but we don't camp there.

00:13:26.513 --> 00:13:35.919
You pick yourself back up. And that's what the Lord's wanting. His goodness and His mercy are so good.

00:13:35.920 --> 00:13:47.039
You don't want to live in sin because His goodness and mercy pulled me out of it. I don't want to stay in the pit.

00:13:47.040 --> 00:13:54.125
If you're living there, I really challenge you; I really question your thermostat of where your salvation is.

00:13:54.126 --> 00:14:02.638
He's coming back for the ten virgins, right? Five had their lamps full and five were empty.

00:14:02.639 --> 00:14:22.799
Five had to go look for it. And in Revelation 19, he talks about the bride that is seeking Him. Revelation 19. He talks about the bride looking for it.

00:14:22.800 --> 00:14:38.559
"Let us rejoice and be glad and give Him glory, for the wedding of the Lamb has come, and His bride has made herself ready."The bride was already in pursuit.

00:14:38.560 --> 00:14:47.438
She was looking for Him. He said there's a big difference between where the church is right now.

00:14:47.439 --> 00:14:57.887
A lot of the church doesn't have an expectation for the return of the Lord. The bride's not making herself ready.

00:14:57.888 --> 00:15:03.278
You're hearing about prosperity and building your kingdom on this earth.

00:15:03.279 --> 00:15:14.592
You don't have an expectation. The bride's not even looking for Him. So, I like what he was saying about Revelation 19:7.

00:15:14.593 --> 00:15:24.159
He said, "The bride is making herself ready."The bride has an expectation of the return of the groom.

00:15:24.160 --> 00:15:30.198
She's preparing herself. Are you preparing yourself for the coming of the Lord?

00:15:30.199 --> 00:15:35.745
Are you preparing yourself for what you're about to experience?

00:15:35.746 --> 00:15:42.919
Are you the virgins that have their lamps full of oil? Or are you the virgins that are just like, "You know what?

00:15:42.920 --> 00:15:47.599
We know He's coming and we'll wait until the day He comes,"and then it's too late?

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:54.615
The bridegroom came when you were out trying to get your lamps full. You must remain at a place of full.

00:15:54.616 --> 00:16:03.599
And that's why He always talks about, "Let your full fight for you."You've got to get in a place where your full is always fighting.

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:10.028
What you're full of will come out of you. What are you expecting in these last days?

00:16:10.029 --> 00:16:14.978
Let your full fight for you in these last days. Don't remain empty.

00:16:14.979 --> 00:16:20.372
You've got to keep your lamp full of oil in these last days for what's about to happen.

00:16:20.373 --> 00:16:26.958
There were five that had it ready and five that didn't. Five were taken, five are left.

00:16:26.959 --> 00:16:37.907
I truly believe in the first round there'll be—I believe there are two different catching-aways.

00:16:37.908 --> 00:16:46.958
Now, I'm not here to argue theology, but I believe this one's going to shock everyone, the ones that didn't have their lamps full of oil.

00:16:46.959 --> 00:16:52.729
But the ones that are the bride, that are preparing herself, will be caught up with Him.

00:16:52.730 --> 00:17:05.279
We're going to go in the rapture—the first round—the ones that are full, the ones that are letting their full fight for them, the ones that are keeping their eyes on Jesus, the ones that have their lamps ready.

00:17:05.280 --> 00:17:18.738
The bride is in hot pursuit of the groom. You didn't have to warn her because, "I'm not real excited about the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:17:18.739 --> 00:17:27.850
I really want to get married and have babies and a career, but I'm not really in pursuit of Him."I don't really care because your eyes are focused on something else.

00:17:27.851 --> 00:17:46.301
But for the groom, I'm telling you, Diana, when we were together, I always looked at her and said, "Baby, you look beautiful today."My eyes, even after all these years, I look at her and say, "You look so beautiful tonight, honey.""Well, honey, you've seen me every day of your life."I know, but you look exceptional today.

00:17:46.302 --> 00:17:53.633
I'm still in pursuit of my wife. I still love my wife. You have to be in pursuit; don't allow your marriage to grow dull.

00:17:53.634 --> 00:18:04.944
You can't allow your marriage to die. Keep that pursuit. Be ye imitators of God as dear children; imitate their father. As you look to Him, I want to be more like Him.

00:18:04.945 --> 00:18:16.639
And as I listen to elders, I go, "I am so far from this."I don't even know if I'm ever going to get halfway close to what has been in some of these people's ministries.

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:26.239
But God, I'm imitating You, and I'm in hot pursuit of You. And I know that those that seek Me will find Me; those that knock, I'll open the door unto them.

00:18:26.240 --> 00:18:33.599
And I believe, you know what, I've got a long way to go, but maybe a short time to get there, right?

00:18:33.600 --> 00:18:43.519
But I know that inside, as I keep seeking Him, I'll find Him. But I want to encourage you tonight, as I say all of this, be imitators of God.

00:18:43.520 --> 00:18:50.959
Pursue Him with all your heart. Keep your lamps full. Have an expectation that He's coming back.

00:18:50.960 --> 00:19:03.678
He could come back tomorrow; He could come back by the end of the year, by September, by the Shemitah, by Rosh Hashanah.

00:19:03.679 --> 00:19:12.719
What about a revival? I'm believing, but I'm always in pursuit of Him.

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:19.119
Keep your lamps full tonight. Always seek Jesus with all your heart.

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:29.466
Don't let a day go by without saying, "Jesus, I love You. I'm so glad You're in my life. I'm so glad You came to save me. I'm so glad You redeemed me.

00:19:29.467 --> 00:19:36.049
I'm so glad You set me free by Your blood, by what You did on that cross for me."That's why I take communion every day.

00:19:36.050 --> 00:19:41.284
I take it all the time. I've got buckets of it. Why? It's not a religious act to me; this is about relationship.

00:19:41.285 --> 00:19:58.319
I want to know Him. And once I get it, I don't want to lose it. I don't want to taste and see that the Lord is good and then just visit it and have just a residue of it.

00:19:58.320 --> 00:20:03.617
I want it to be imparted inside of me so that whenever people see it, it's like Moses—his face is glowing.

00:20:03.618 --> 00:20:06.649
They have to put a veil over his face because people are freaking out.

00:20:06.650 --> 00:20:11.038
"What's going on with Brandon?"I have been with the Master.

00:20:11.039 --> 00:20:17.199
I have been with my King. He's my friend. He is my everything.

00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:25.869
And that light shines out of me, every pore, every fiber of my being, that I've tasted and I have seen that the Lord is good.

00:20:25.870 --> 00:20:35.167
Once you taste and you touch the hem of His garment and you get a little bit of the anointing and you get a little bit of the glory on you, there's nothing better.

00:20:35.168 --> 00:20:40.719
There's nothing more that will change your life other than to keep touching. You pursue it.

00:20:40.720 --> 00:21:00.010
I question people's authenticity because once you have tasted and you have seen, once you've experienced the glory, once you see your daughter that wasn't able to go to the bathroom and was bound up for weeks and swelled up and the doctors have all these things and God touches her and she doesn't have to have a diaper on anymore...

00:21:00.011 --> 00:21:05.439
once you taste and see that the Lord is good, there's nothing else that matters.

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:11.918
That's what I said last night. I'm dead to it. I can say whatever He wants me to say.

00:21:11.919 --> 00:21:18.399
If the platform goes away, I'm bold about what He says. I question, do you believe what the Lord is saying to me?

00:21:18.400 --> 00:21:21.611
I believe it's something different. It's a new generation.

00:21:21.612 --> 00:21:33.599
You're the one crying in the wilderness like John the Baptist did the first time, warning the people that Jesus was coming and all the things that were happening, right?

00:21:33.600 --> 00:21:42.353
We're doing it again. He's coming again. He's coming back for His church. There's a major move of God happening.

00:21:42.354 --> 00:21:49.319
What are you anticipating in your life as you see the signs of the times and the coming Lord Jesus Christ all around you?

00:21:49.320 --> 00:22:02.079
I give you the hope that there is a shaking to awaken. He's bringing the bride to His side. What side are you on? You can choose today.

00:22:02.080 --> 00:22:08.158
I want to be on His side and He has a plan for my life, or you can be the ones that are going to get the spanking.

00:22:08.159 --> 00:22:13.839
I don't want to be in that group. I want to be on the right side of things.

00:22:13.840 --> 00:22:18.158
So, I want to show you today shakings that are happening right now.

00:22:18.159 --> 00:22:35.987
You can see it in the news, but I love Revelation 19:7: "Let us rejoice and be glad and give glory."Give Him glory, for the wedding of the Lamb has come and His bride has made herself ready today.

00:22:35.988 --> 00:22:41.918
The bride is in pursuit, and is she looking for Him? Are you looking?

00:22:41.919 --> 00:22:53.839
Have you made yourself ready? All right, go ahead. Show them.

00:22:53.840 --> 00:23:06.879
And this is what's happening in today's news. We have a major earthquake in Venezuela.

00:23:06.880 --> 00:23:16.151
A major 7.5 earthquake happened in Venezuela today. A shaking is coming to South America.

00:23:16.152 --> 00:23:21.581
A 7.5 and then a 7.2 right in the same area. Two in the same day.

00:23:21.582 --> 00:23:31.918
And then there was a 5.6 in California. Did it happen by Malibu? I have to look. 5.6.

00:23:31.919 --> 00:23:42.959
And then there was—because God said, "I'm going to shake Malibu"and it'll be a sign—a 6.9 in Japan today.

00:23:42.960 --> 00:23:50.079
The Lord said, "I'm going to shake Malibu. I'm going to shake California."I want to know, did that happen by there?

00:23:50.080 --> 00:24:01.439
That's interesting. I'm looking for it all the time for Malibu to be shaken.

00:24:01.440 --> 00:24:09.678
Okay, they felt it in Colombia, they said. Well, they felt it all over the place.

00:24:09.679 --> 00:24:15.778
Big earthquakes. What does the Lord say? What is this happening with the earth?

00:24:15.779 --> 00:24:24.879
The earth is shaking and rocking and reeling like a drunkard. The Word said it was coming.

00:24:24.880 --> 00:24:32.384
And so we're seeing the beginnings of it, the birthing pains. What are we about to see? Major shaking. Why?

00:24:32.385 --> 00:24:42.939
Because I told you Colombia will be shaken, Venezuela will be shaken, Cuba will be shaken. As we saw earthquakes, Cuba will be shaken. Why?

00:24:42.940 --> 00:24:49.678
Because it's a representation of what's happening, and in the spiritual realm, it is manifesting in the natural.

00:24:49.679 --> 00:24:56.216
And a great harvest of souls is coming to Venezuela, Cuba, and Colombia.

00:24:56.217 --> 00:24:59.979
Watch. And it's going to spread through Brazil. Watch what happens.

00:24:59.980 --> 00:25:05.119
God is going to pour out His Spirit on South America. Watch. Now look at this.

00:25:05.120 --> 00:25:13.678
Where is that earthquake at? They're saying it's not. Well, that's a bummer.

00:25:13.679 --> 00:25:21.323
It's coming. That's San Francisco, so it's further up north. One is down south.

